{"tid":1494141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家有心理準備","createTime":"2019-08-21T14:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T14:33:10.000Z","uid":69845,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6e8d90a262302412d2a25386c69ea90168567a","tid":1494141,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"8.18後<br />\n<br />\n170萬人遊行 無分和勇 齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺上覺得大家嘅危機感低咗<br />\n<br />\n請謹記我地仲有好大段路 有升級嘅準備<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日有好一批手足被清算 正正提醒我<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地打緊仗</span><br />\n<br />\n請準備好 加埋9月嘅學生罷課 大家開始準備罷工 <br />\n用呢兩個星期時間做文宣同對策 <br />\n<br />\n集會 遊行 遊擊 文宣 攬炒行動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開波啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n有好人支持緊我地  <br />\n<br />\n離世義士 數以百計嘅被捕手足 無數受傷嘅義士<br />\n<br />\n攬炒團隊 海外香港人  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqOv0KJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqOv0KJ.jpg&h=e454ac33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5T7TYwp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5T7TYwp.jpg&h=66bd20c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUv2RRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUv2RRp.jpg&h=c3608cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1PWbRq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1PWbRq.jpg&h=b467af75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dJcuC6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dJcuC6.png&h=445633b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"c44b9ffa331dfdaabab5bd487459976ca9d316a3","tid":1494141,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:11:10.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n<br />\n818<br />\n